<p><a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/13/24099402/openai-text-to-video-ai-sora-public-availability" target="_blank">https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/13/24099402/openai-text-to-video-ai-sora-public-availability</a></p>
<div><ul><li><a href="/ai-artificial-intelligence">Artificial Intelligence</a><span>/</span></li><li><a href="/tech">Tech</a></li></ul><h1>OpenAI’s Sora text-to-video generator will be publicly available later this year</h1><div><div><div><h1>OpenAI’s Sora text-to-video generator will be publicly available later this year</h1><span><span> / </span><h2>OpenAI CTO Mira Murati tells The Wall Street Journal that Sora will eventually incorporate sound as well.</h2></span></div><div><div><p><span>By</span> <span> <span><a href="/authors/emma-roth">Emma Roth</a></span><span>, <span>a news writer who covers the streaming wars, consumer tech, crypto, social media, and much more. Previously, she was a writer and editor at MUO. </span></span></span></p></div><div><time datetime="2024-03-13T13:37:28.046Z"> Mar 13, 2024, 1:37 PM UTC</time></div><div><div><div><h2>Share this story</h2><ul><li><button aria-label="Copy link"><svg viewBox="0 0 30 30" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M13.7876 20.18C12.6943 21.2733 10.9133 21.2733 9.81998 20.18C8.72669 19.0867 8.72666 17.3056 9.81998 16.2123L12.0243 14.0081C13.1176 12.9147 14.8986 12.9147 15.9919 14.0081C16.0816 14.0954 16.1326 14.2149 16.1335 14.34C16.1343 14.4651 16.085 14.5854 15.9965 14.6739C15.9081 14.7624 15.7877 14.8118 15.6627 14.8109C15.5376 14.81 15.418 14.759 15.3306 14.6693C14.5922 13.9309 13.4239 13.9309 12.6855 14.6693L10.4812 16.8736C9.74277 17.6121 9.74277 18.7803 10.4812 19.5188C11.2197 20.2572 12.3879 20.2571 13.1264 19.5188L15.2204 17.4246V17.4247C15.3077 17.335 15.4273 17.284 15.5525 17.2832C15.6776 17.2823 15.7978 17.3317 15.8863 17.4202C15.9747 17.5087 16.0241 17.6289 16.0232 17.7541C16.0224 17.8792 15.9714 17.9987 15.8817 18.086L13.7876 20.18ZM17.9757 15.9919C16.8824 17.0852 15.1014 17.0852 14.0081 15.9919V15.992C13.9184 15.9047 13.8674 15.7852 13.8665 15.6601C13.8658 15.5349 13.915 15.4147 14.0035 15.3262C14.092 15.2377 14.2123 15.1883 14.3374 15.1892C14.4626 15.19 14.582 15.241 14.6694 15.3307C15.40